PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1998-1008 which will extend the deadline for signing AGREEMENTS with the Provinces concerning the VOCATIONAL REHABILITATION OF DISABLED PERSONS for the 1996-97 and 1997-98 fiscal years, from October 31, 1998 to December 31, 1998.
